                      ],
                      "text": "October 2, 2021",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "The passing of time is marked by meals as we drink and make merry, blessed by nature's grace. From past to present, the years go by in the blink of an eye. Smoke of hearths brings us joy and domesticity paints a picture of everyday life. Delicate clouds chase the moon as the boat floats on the river of time.",
