                      ],
                      "text": "January 6, 2022",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "A strange tale that tells of adeptal affinity, where things are no longer what they once were, save for the thousands of threads of sorrow.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "The opera sings about the feats of a heroine, with new lines added to the story, and told anew in many homes.",
